node.text:
Swipe for smiles 😇 
Things have been toughhhh the past few months. A yo-yo of emotions, mental growth, constant injuries that have made me feel incapable, anxiety and feeling so unsure of what the hells going on in the world. It really is hard to show your true life through Instagram photos and stories, and it’s honestly sooo true when people say you never know what someone is going through & Instagram is definitely a highlight reel

So many people are struggling every day and I’m becoming more and more aware of how your attitude can literally change someone’s day. Just a reminder to be kind to strangers and those close to you, never go out of your way to hurt someone or judge based on something so surface level

I am super positive despite anything I have going on, I’m always wanting to do more and be more. So I hope I can encourage you all to find the positives in your day & life, zoom out, there are so many ☀️🦋🦋
